values.comment:
 Move the content box by a relative distance.

Given a model where

    getPosition model == { x = 10, y = 20 }

the following holds

    getPosition (model |> moveBy { x = -15, y = 5 }) == { x = -5, y = 25 }

 Move the content box to a point.

Given a model where

    getPosition model == { x = 10, y = 20 }

the following holds

    getPosition (model |> moveTo { x = -15, y = 5 }) == { x = -15, y = 5 }

